<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_421_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / . Als Jr vns nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd wir ew <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l4"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eins <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tages <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l5">Hanaw 
<del rend="strikethrough">beÿ </del> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> beÿ ew in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> meſſe cʒeſüchen / . vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l7">als Jr vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / daʒ Jr Jn den 
<add><ab facs="#facs_421_r1l6">Acht </ab></add> tag vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l8"><expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſolt / . <expan>Laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr erſame <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l9">daʒ wir die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> cʒü ew <expan>cʒeſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> mainen / daʒ die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l10">beÿ ew ſein auf den <expan>Mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Palmtag nu ſchirſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l11">cʒü <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> tagcʒeit 
<del rend="strikethrough">da cʒe ſein </del> vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr das <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l12"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw alſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> vvöllet / vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> </ab>
